{"tid":532022,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[樹大招風]有無人覺得任賢齊演得好過林家棟？","createTime":"2018-01-17T11:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T15:10:39.000Z","uid":5375,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"079d795b7c0ba26a99daa770a80942e21328311b","tid":532022,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"我本身對小齊個印象麻麻，因為佢以前大部分戲/歌俾人個感覺都係鳩鳩地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n但樹大招風入面演一個氣傲又自以為是既賊王，由霸氣到慢慢收山轉行，係共產黨之下笑笑口忍氣吞聲幾年，最後都係故態復萌，中間既心態轉變拿捏得好自然，角色又結合到佢啲濕鳩口音。結局因為一道氣殺警，之後訓低跌左支AK想執返但又執唔到，個個CLOSE SHOT已經夠拎影帝<br />\n<br />\n林家棟當然都演得好好，獨角戲同黑仔既對手戲都好屈機，但我覺得好多演員都可以做到。陳小春都演得好，貪都出晒面，但唔夠細膩。<br />\n<br />\n馬後炮，獎就一定唔會俾小齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，林家棟係影壇付出咁多，呢套都演得好，都值得拎影帝，只不過我就覺得任賢齊發揮得更好。<br />\n<br />\n點睇？"},{"pid":"dc43532458a0db411a73d74356820ff13fac6c0f","tid":532022,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770fc604d7c5adf8d99eb7d2203a40e86e552402","tid":532022,"uid":36432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:06:29.000Z","msg":"林家棟最後同黑仔嗰場戲太出色無計"},{"pid":"594275620029f2c1ee5398184040214e171c97a0","tid":532022,"uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"最好都係陳政協"},{"pid":"33862829755df7b3a4af17d646b16f25f211868a","tid":532022,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"594275620029f2c1ee5398184040214e171c97a0","tid":532022,"uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"最好都係陳政協"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ok"},{"pid":"1aade719ade09e9ab75ef00c58ff4ba24f132201","tid":532022,"uid":5375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"770fc604d7c5adf8d99eb7d2203a40e86e